import React, { useState, useEffect, useRef } from 'react'; import './styles.css'; // Include this file for styling (defined below) const Sidebar = () => { const [isOpen, setIsOpen] = useState(false); // Manage sidebar visibility state const sidebarRef = useRef(null); // Reference for the sidebar element const toggleButtonRef = useRef(null); // Reference for the toggle button const toggleSidebar = () => { setIsOpen(!isOpen); // Toggle the state between true and false }; useEffect(() => { const handleClickOutside = (event) => { if ( sidebarRef.current && !sidebarRef.current.contains(event.target) && toggleButtonRef.current && !toggleButtonRef.current.contains(event.target) ) { setIsOpen(false); // Close sidebar if clicked outside } }; document.addEventListener('mousedown', handleClickOutside); return () => { document.removeEventListener('mousedown', handleClickOutside); }; }, []); return (
